n January. Shares have fallen 27.61% YTD on the back of accounting misconduct within their Nutrition</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2166482982/image_2166482982.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742738-adm-tough-2024-2025-should-be-better", "pub_date": "2024-12-07 07:49:36"}, {"id": "4742749", "title": "India's IPO Market Set For Another High After Landmark Year For Fundraising", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1071665030/image_1071665030.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Indiann 50 Rupees new currency with 10 reupee coins on isolated whie background\" data-id=\"1071665030\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"6000px\" height=\"4000px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1071665030/image_1071665030.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1071665030/image_1071665030.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1071665030/image_1071665030.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1071665030/image_1071665030.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1071665030/image_1071665030.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1071665030/image_1071665030.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1071665030/image_1071665030.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1071665030/image_1071665030.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">lakshmiprasad S</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Fundraising via IPOs in India is set for another landmark year after economic growth, favorable market conditions and improvements in the regulatory framework helped companies raise record amounts in 2024.</p> <p>A total of 298 companies listed on</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1071665030/image_1071665030.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742749-india-ipo-market-set-for-another-high-after-landmark-year-for-fundraising", "pub_date": "2024-12-07 07:45:00"}, {"id": "4742736", "title": "Lindt & Spr\u00fcngli: The Valuation Remains A Sticking Point", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458953977/image_458953977.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Lindt Easter Gold Bunny on Shelf\" data-id=\"458953977\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1028px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458953977/image_458953977.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458953977/image_458953977.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458953977/image_458953977.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458953977/image_458953977.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458953977/image_458953977.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458953977/image_458953977.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458953977/image_458953977.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458953977/image_458953977.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">DWithers/iStock Unreleased via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Premium chocolatier <strong>Chocoladefabriken Lindt &amp; Spr\u00fcngli AG </strong>(<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/LDSVF\" title=\"Chocoladefabriken Lindt &amp; Spr\u00fcngli AG\">OTCPK:LDSVF</a>) (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/COCXF\" title=\"Chocoladefabriken Lindt &amp; Spr\u00fcngli AG Participation Certificates\">OTCPK:COCXF</a>) (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/CHLSY\" title=\"Chocoladefabriken Lindt &amp; Spr\u00fcngli AG\">OTCPK:CHLSY</a>) hasn't had it easy recently. Cost inflation has been an issue for the industry, and the stock has been somewhat moribund</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458953977/image_458953977.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742736-lindt-and-sprngli-stock-valuation-remains-sticking-point", "pub_date": "2024-12-07 07:32:00"}, {"id": "4742742", "title": "Markets Weekly Outlook - Central Bank Focus As U.S. Inflation Looms", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1251664775/image_1251664775.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Dark metal percentage sign\" data-id=\"1251664775\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1075px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1251664775/image_1251664775.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1251664775/image_1251664775.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1251664775/image_1251664775.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1251664775/image_1251664775.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1251664775/image_1251664775.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1251664775/image_1251664775.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1251664775/image_1251664775.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1251664775/image_1251664775.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">peterschreiber.media/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>By Zain Vawda</em></p> <h2><strong>Week in Review: Jobs Data All but Confirms a December Rate Cut</strong></h2> <p>A week that saw a lot of choppy price action as markets awaited the US jobs report on Friday. A stellar jobs</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1251664775/image_1251664775.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742742-markets-weekly-outlook-central-bank-focus-us-inflation-looms", "pub_date": "2024-12-07 07:20:00"}, {"id": "4742735", "title": "Lightspeed: Brighter Now Than In 2021", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1473939572/image_1473939572.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Customer feedback improve business to growth continuously. Japanese barista in apron standing in the cashier counter and give the customer bill with smile at the coffee shop. Customer looking at the bill and make payment\" data-id=\"1473939572\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1473939572/image_1473939572.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1473939572/image_1473939572.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1473939572/image_1473939572.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1473939572/image_1473939572.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1473939572/image_1473939572.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1473939572/image_1473939572.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1473939572/image_1473939572.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1473939572/image_1473939572.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Patamaporn Umnahanant/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Today, <strong>Lightspeed Commerce</strong> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/LSPD\" title=\"Lightspeed Commerce Inc.\">LSPD</a></span>, <span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">TSX:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/LSPD:CA\" title=\"Lightspeed Commerce Inc.\">LSPD:CA</a></span>) offers more than point-of-sale (POS) systems. They have expanded their offerings, with a focus on their payment solutions. Now, they are offering it together as a unified offering, which aims to simplify managing</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1473939572/image_1473939572.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742735-lightspeed-brighter-now-than-in-2021", "pub_date": "2024-12-07 07:10:43"}, {"id": "4742732", "title": "Regions Financial: NIM Expansion Offset By Slow Asset Growth (Rating Upgrade)", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/601359624/image_601359624.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Regions Financial Corporation Retail Consumer Location I\" data-id=\"601359624\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/601359624/image_601359624.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/601359624/image_601359624.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/601359624/image_601359624.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/601359624/image_601359624.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/601359624/image_601359624.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/601359624/image_601359624.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/601359624/image_601359624.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/601359624/image_601359624.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">jetcityimage</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Shares of Regions Financial (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/RF\" title=\"Regions Financial Corporation\">RF</a></span>) have been a strong performer over the past year, gaining 53%. I have been overly cautious on this company, preferring other regional banks to RF. Since my last write-up in <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4663038-regions-financial-q4-earnings-preview-deposit-stabilization-essential\">January</a></p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/601359624/image_601359624.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742732-regions-financial-nim-expansion-offset-by-slow-asset-growth-upgrade", "pub_date": "2024-12-07 07:02:00"}, {"id": "4742739", "title": "The Recipe For A Top-Performing Value Strategy Requires Different Ingredients", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593728/image_1072593728.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Little piggy banks on ascending stacks of coins\" data-id=\"1072593728\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5423px\" height=\"3261px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593728/image_1072593728.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593728/image_1072593728.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593728/image_1072593728.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593728/image_1072593728.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593728/image_1072593728.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593728/image_1072593728.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593728/image_1072593728.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593728/image_1072593728.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">PM Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>By Christopher Gannatti, CFA</em></p> <p>How do you beat the market?<sup>1</sup> For many investors, this is among the first questions that leap to mind and a motivating reason that attracts them to the craft of investing.</p> <p>However, it is one</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593728/image_1072593728.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742739-recipe-top-performing-value-strategy-requires-different-ingredients", "pub_date": "2024-12-07 07:00:00"}, {"id": "4742730", "title": "IVOL: Abandoning Ship (Rating Downgrade)", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1320226467/image_1320226467.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Piggy bank in a volatile position\" data-id=\"1320226467\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1320226467/image_1320226467.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1320226467/image_1320226467.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1320226467/image_1320226467.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1320226467/image_1320226467.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1320226467/image_1320226467.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1320226467/image_1320226467.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1320226467/image_1320226467.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1320226467/image_1320226467.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw 